OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunny spells
OL,6,Fwith occasional high-level cloud to
OL,7,Fend the day. Some low cloud and fog is
OL,8,Fexpected to move in from the North Sea
OL,9,Fovernight and spread slowly across
OL,10,FEast Anglia. A warm night for most,
OL,11,Fcooler along the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FEarly morning low cloud
OL,14,Fquickly burning back, turning sunny by
OL,15,Fthe afternoon before low cloud returns
OL,16,Fin a freshening northeasterly wind.
OL,17,FTemperatures very warm inland but
OL,18,Fcooler along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
