OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,6,Fmorning low cloud quickly burning
OL,7,Fback, turning sunny by the afternoon
OL,8,Fon Sunday. Dry with plenty of sunshine
OL,9,Fon Monday. Cloudy periods on Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith showers possible.
